These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, fanta, 7up, milk
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: parkour, rugby, skiing, golf
1. the person who's sport is parkour is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is skiing##5
2. the person drinking fanta is not the person who's sport is parkour##6
3. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the person who's sport is golf##1
4. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1
5. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person who's sport is parkour##1
6. the person who's sport is parkour is not the person drinking 7up##6

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1      |    2     |    3     |    4    |
| Beverage   | fanta   | milk    | coffee    | 7up |
| Sport      | golf | parkour | skiing | rugby |

