.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, 7up, tea, water
There 4 different types of food: avocado, apple, banana, lemon
1. the person eating avocado is on the far right##1
2. the person drinking 7up is somewhere to the left of the person drinking tea##5
3. the person eating lemon is somewhere to the left of the person drinking water##5
4. the person drinking 7up is not the person eating apple##6
5. the person eating lemon is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
6. the person eating avocado is on the right of the person eating banana##1
7. the person drinking water is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
8. the person drinking tea is somewhere to the left of the person drinking cola##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |     2      |    3     |     4     |
| Beverage   | 7up  | tea    | cola | water    |
| Food       | lemon | apple | banana  | avocado |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: tea, 7up, juice, almond-milk
The people have 4 different jobs:  librarian, nurse, entrepreneur, musician
1. the person drinking almond-milk is not the librarian##6
2. the nurse is not the person drinking juice##6
3. the entrepreneur is on the left or right of the person drinking 7up##3
4. the nurse is the person drinking tea##1
5. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the nurse##1
6. the person drinking tea is in an odd position##4
7. the librarian is on the far left or far right##3
8. the entrepreneur is somewhere to the left of the musician##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |       2        |   3    |   4    |
| Beverage   | almond-milk       | 7up  | tea  | juice |
| Job        | entrepreneur | musician | nurse | librarian  |

