.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-4::.
4 different pets are kept: dog, ferret, turtle, lizard
The people use 4 different means of transport: snowmobile, airplane, ship, boat
1. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
2. the owner of the ferret is somewhere to the left of the person driving the snowmobile##5
3. the person driving the boat is not the owner of the ferret##6
4. the person driving the boat is somewhere to the right of the person driving the snowmobile##5
5. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person driving the airplane##1
6. the owner of the lizard is somewhere to the left of the person driving the boat##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |     3     |    4     |
| Pet         | ferret | turtle | lizard     | dog |
| Transport   | airplane     | ship    | snowmobile | boat    |

