.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: tea, lemonade, coffee, mirinda
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, train, jet-ski, taxi
1. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
2. the person drinking mirinda is somewhere to the left of the person driving the jet-ski##5
3. the person drinking mirinda is somewhere to the left of the person driving the train##5
4. the person drinking lemonade is not the person driving the taxi##6
5. the person driving the helicopter is not the person drinking tea##6
6. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
7. the person driving the jet-ski is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |  2   |    3     |   4   |
| Beverage    | tea        | mirinda | coffee | lemonade |
| Transport   | taxi | helicopter | train     | jet-ski   |

