.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-6::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: zombie, drama, family, adventure
There are 4 different nationalities: british, argentine, french, malaysian
1. the british is on the right of the person watching zombie movies##1
2. the person watching adventure movies is not the argentine##6
3. the british is on the far right##1
4. the argentine is somewhere to the right of the malaysian##5
5. the person watching family movies is the person watching family movies##1
6. the person watching family movies is somewhere to the left of the british##5
7. the person watching family movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching zombie movies##5
8. the person watching drama movies is somewhere to the left of the malaysian##5
9. the person watching drama movies is somewhere to the left of the malaysian##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |     3     |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | drama | family    | zombie  | adventure   |
| Nationality   | french  | malaysian | argentine | british |

