.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-7::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: horror, adventure, fantasy, western
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: dubstep, techno, jazz, folk
1. the fan jazz is on the left or right of the fan dubstep##3
2. the fan jazz is not the person watching adventure movies##6
3. the person watching horror movies is the fan techno##1
4. the fan dubstep is on the left or right of the fan folk##3
5. the fan jazz is on the far left##1
6. the person watching adventure movies is the fan dubstep##1
7. the person watching western movies is somewhere to the left of the fan dubstep##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |      3      |      4      |
| Movie-Genre   | western | adventure     | fantasy | horror |
| Music-Genre   | jazz | dubstep | folk      | techno         |

