2. the videographer is somewhere to the left of the freelancer##5
3. the videographer is on the right of the teacher##1
4. the teacher is on the left or right of the person drinking fanta##3
5. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left or right of the teacher##3
6. the manager is on the left or right of the person drinking lemonade##3
7. the person drinking cola is somewhere to the right of the person drinking iced-tea##5
8. the person drinking fanta is not the videographer##6

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |     2      |       3       |      4       |
| Beverage   | fanta  | lemonade        | iced-tea      | cola          |
| Job        | manager | teacher | videographer | freelancer |

