The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, roller, bike, motorbike
1. the dancer is in an odd position##4
2. the person driving the roller is not the chef##6
3. the person driving the boat is somewhere to the right of the doctor##5
4. the person driving the motorbike is in an even position##4
5. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person driving the bike##1
6. the person driving the motorbike is the doctor##1
7. the dancer is not the person driving the motorbike##6
8. the analyst is somewhere to the right of the chef##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4     |
| Job         | dancer  | doctor | chef    | analyst |
| Transport   | roller | motorbike | bike | boat  |

