.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-10::.
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, turtle, frog, pony
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, soccer, rowing, snowboarding
1. the person who's sport is badminton is not the owner of the chinchilla##6
2. the owner of the pony is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
3. the person who's sport is snowboarding is the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
4. the owner of the pony is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
5. the owner of the frog is not the person who's sport is snowboarding##6
6. the person who's sport is soccer is not the owner of the turtle##6
7. the person who's sport is snowboarding is in an even position##4
8. the owner of the frog is the person who's sport is badminton##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |       2       |    3    |    4     |
| Pet     | frog | chinchilla        | pony  | turtle     |
| Sport   | badminton     | snowboarding | soccer | rowing |

