.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-11::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: photography, card-games, collecting, gardening
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: dubstep, punk, salsa, classical
1. the person who's hobby is photography is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is gardening##3
2. the fan punk is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is photography##5
3. the fan salsa is not the person who's hobby is collecting##6
4. the person who's hobby is card-games is between the fan classical and the person who's hobby is collecting##2
5. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
6. the fan punk is between the fan dubstep and the person who's hobby is photography##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |   3   |     4     |
| Hobby         | collecting | card-games    | photography | gardening |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep         | punk | classical   | salsa     |

