4. the person driving the car is on the right of the person eating zucchini##1
5. the person driving the skateboard is not the person eating kiwi##6
6. the person eating zucchini is not the person driving the helicopter##6
7. the person eating nectarine is somewhere to the left of the person eating zucchini##5
8. the person eating orange is on the left of the person eating nectarine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |     3     |   4    |
| Food        | orange  | nectarine | zucchini | kiwi |
