2. the person eating papaya is not the person watching superhero movies##6
3. the person eating apricot is the person watching horror movies##1
4. the person eating cherry is somewhere to the right of the person watching superhero movies##5
5. the person eating apricot is between the person eating papaya and the person watching comedy movies##2
6. the person eating papaya is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Food          | kale | papaya      | apricot | cherry   |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero     | drama | horror   | comedy |

