2. the owner of the rat is somewhere to the right of the owner of the frog##5
3. the owner of the frog is on the left of the owner of the rat##1
4. the owner of the cat is not the person who's hobby is traveling##6
5. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is between the person who's hobby is traveling and the person who's hobby is photography##2
6. the person who's hobby is baking is on the far left or far right##3
7. the person who's hobby is baking is on the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
8. the owner of the cat is somewhere to the right of the owner of the frog##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2     |      3      |      4      |
| Hobby   | photography | magic-tricks | traveling | baking |
| Pet     | turtle  | frog      | rat  | cat       |

